  "brief_justification": "This is an integrative literature review analyzing the theoretical evolution of the social management (gestao social) field in Brazil, drawing on articles from the SPELL database (2010-2020). The paper employs a qualitative, systematic review methodology (following Torraco 2005 and Botelho et al. 2011) to map concepts, theoretical categories, and epistemological/ontological assumptions. It contains no quantitative data analysis, no statistical tests, and makes no causal claims.",
